  "body": "Tested against current master a0f294e550e9369bab711d9ae4ec79c942eeb792.\r\n\r\nAny truncated message will be responded with a FormErr by plugin/forward, due to a state mismatch https://github.com/coredns/coredns/blob/a0f294e550e9369bab711d9ae4ec79c942eeb792/plugin/forward/forward.go#L133-L137\r\n\r\nThat's the result of the proxy implementation always returning `nil` if miekg/dns returns an error, even it's just the pseudo `ErrTruncated`. That affects the implementation in `truncated()` and later on in `Match()`. https://github.com/coredns/coredns/blob/a0f294e550e9369bab711d9ae4ec79c942eeb792/plugin/forward/connect.go#L69\r\n\r\nIt'd be great to see more test coverage in the plugin/forward implementation given its growing complexity.",
